title: Bobby’s Mailbag: Should You Delete Instagram Pictures Of Your Ex? + Famous Johns Draft + Dierks Bentley Picks His Own 'Scratch' Songs
itunes:title: Bobby’s Mailbag: Should You Delete Instagram Pictures Of Your Ex? + Famous Johns Draft + Dierks Bentley Picks His Own 'Scratch' Songs
description:
Bobby read an email from a listener who wants to ask his girlfriend to delete pictures of her ex from her Instagram account. We do our Fantasy Draft on ‘Famous Johns’ and we talk to Dierks Bentley on his 19th No. 1, getting recognized from TV and the one song he would eliminate from his concerts if he had to pick.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
